Now we need to go into <blockquote>ActionHandler.java</blockquote> and Underneath [code]firstClickObject[/code] add this;

	[code]	case 3192:
		c.highscores();
		break;[/code]

Finally we need to make the Highscores clickable within the radious of 7 squares or how many you like.

Go into <blockquote>ClickObject.java</blockquote> and underneath [code]public class ClickObject implements PacketType {[/code] add;

				[code]  case 3192:
					c.objectDistance = 7;
				break;[/code]

